HEALTHCARE COMPLIANCE NOTICE

This software is designed for healthcare interface testing and development 
purposes only. Users are responsible for:

1. HIPAA Compliance: Ensuring any PHI is properly de-identified before use
2. Vendor Compatibility: Verifying generated messages meet vendor requirements
3. Production Testing: Thoroughly testing in non-production environments
4. Data Validation: Ensuring synthetic data meets clinical requirements

This tool generates synthetic data only and should never be used with real
patient health information (PHI).

